layout.p:
Columns: 14;
                                                  ruled lines: 35;
                                                  written lines: 35; Uniform layout. Ruling by hard point,
membrane by membrane. Four columns per membrane, each written within decorated engravings.  Three tagin on שעטנזגץ, and the letter ח arched throughout. Several majuscular and minuscular letters. The names of the sons of Haman arranged in 11 lines, in accordance with the rule. The letter ע in the last line is flourished. Wooden rollers (592mm high).
